title: Winning numbers drawn in 'DC 5 Midday' game

maintext:
WASHINGTON (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Dist. of Columbia Lottery’s “DC 5 Midday” game were:
5-9-4-5-3
(five, nine, four, five, three)
